      "id": "revenue-dashboard",
      "name": "Revenue Dashboard",
      "display_name": "Revenue Dashboard",
      "summary": "The Revenue Dashboard provides a real-time view of the company's financial health by visualizing MRR broken down by subscription tier, usage revenue, churn rate, expansion revenue, and net revenue retention across configurable date ranges. It pulls data from the new invoice_items table through a metrics pipeline that aggregates subscription and usage line items, excludes proration, and surfaces the results in a Figma-styled web interface with interactive charts and filters. Completed in September-October 2024, the dashboard is now live on staging, meeting board requirements for subscription and usage metrics.",
      "status": "completed",
      "time_range": "Oct 2024",
