      "id": "brand-refresh",
      "name": "Brand Refresh",
      "display_name": "Brand Refresh",
      "summary": "The project addressed an outdated visual identity and branding inconsistencies by redesigning the logo, establishing a cohesive color palette, typography system, and motion guidelines, and rebuilding the marketing site to reflect the new brand. The technical work involved logo exploration, creation of a brand book with motion principles, implementing the identity in a Next.js site using Satoshi and Inter fonts, CSS custom properties for colors, a responsive grid, performance-focused image handling (Next.js Image, WebP/AVIF), and achieving high Lighthouse scores (94 performance, LCP 1.8 s). Completed in late November 2024, the new brand and site were launched, the brand book made publicly available, and the site is performing well.",
      "status": "completed",
      "time_range": "Oct-Nov 2024",
